John Noble shot himself in the head on Easter Sunday at the M Resort in Las Vegas . 
  He sent a 270 page package to the Las Vegas Review-Journal explaining why he was going to kill himself . 
  Noble said he lost his lifetime free buffet pass to the casino for harassing female employees in 2013 . 
  He also sent a two hour DVD and a letter wishing harm on the women he blames for his suicide . 
  Noble was banned from the casino after he allegedly stalked his mother . 
  He was arrested for stalking on the day his mother died . 
  The M Resort revoked his lifetime buffet pass in September 2010 after he ' harassed female employees at the buffet'